    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/1102cdf975be22abb76738754177acbb.poster.avif?t=1733917017\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/1102cdf975be22abb76738754177acbb.webm?t=1733917017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/1102cdf975be22abb76738754177acbb.mp4?t=1733917017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🍄  <strong>Gnomdom </strong>是一个点触式拼图游戏，你需要找到被困在各个地方的小小精灵，并帮助他们回到家中。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >帮助小精灵</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/74e9e86fb2003035f77bc2fad390746d.poster.avif?t=1733917017\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/74e9e86fb2003035f77bc2fad390746d.webm?t=1733917017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>🍄  进入一个迷人的世界，这里手绘的视觉效果让每一帧都充满生机。探索一个迷人的宇宙，艺术与游戏玩法在这里交融，呈现出迷人的风格。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >具有挑战性和放松性的拼图</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/a5f9bed6a134d7d40e04e99f91805ca8.poster.avif?t=1733917017\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150490/extras/a5f9bed6a134d7d40e04e99f91805ca8.webm?t=1733917017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>迷人的插图</li><li> 自然环境</li><li> 气氛自然的声音</li><li> 有趣且放松的关卡</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我们是谁?</h2>我们是一个由两个人组成的团队，充满激情和决心。我们正在制作我们的首款游戏，并将我们所有的精力投入其中。尽管我们的人数不多，但我们被创造力和创新（以及金钱）驱动，准备在独立游戏界留下我们的印记。",
